text.text: Daryl was very helpful in helping me choose the perfect art for my home, and was very knowledgeable with sharing his insights and expertise with various artists and their work. Delivery was prompt and the installer also did a meticulous job in hanging the painting. A very positive experience and will return!

text.text: I had a fantastic experience at White Space Gallery. Daryl, the sales representative, was incredibly knowledgeable and supportive throughout the process. He was there every step of the way, ensuring my chosen art piece was perfectly hung on my wall. His professionalism and expertise made the entire experience smooth and enjoyable. Highly recommend this gallery for both great art and excellent service!

text.text: I chanced upon this gallery and decided to enter because the curation of paintings seems so colorful. I had chat with the curator who turned out to be such a friendly and down-to-earth person. She is very knowledgeable about the artists and the meanings behind the works. Do pop by if you're in the area!

text.text: Really nice space with friendly staff! Think her name was Xue Yi (?). Had a long conversation with her regarding the various artworks, and her knowledge of the possible interpretations in addition to her own opinions really make the visit a pleasant one. Highly recommend this place!

text.text: Whenever I come to Tiong Bahru, this quaint gallery is my little escape. They always have ongoing free exhibitions or a rotation of their paintings. Gorgeous space with many cafes nearby.
